name: Ditto
description: Ditto will transform into anything it sees, even inanimate objects.

name: Voltorb
description: Voltorb have very volatile temperaments that induce their explosions

name: Golurk
description: Golurk is extremely powerful, he must have a seal on its chest to keep its internal energy from leaking out

name: Regidrago
description: Regidrago can use Dragon-type moves with greater power than other Pokémon thanks to its body composition

name: Gengar
description: Gengar can cast curses on their victims, simply to immobilize them in extreme agony and pain.

name: Garchomp
description: Garchomp can fly in high velocity of sound in the air when folding their bodies and stretching their wings.

name: Blastoise
description: From the spouts on its shell, Blastoise can fire water bullets with amazing accuracy, able to hit a target more than one hundred and sixty feet away.

name: Blaziken
description: The stronger their foes are, the stronger these flames burn, and the more determined Blaziken are to defeat them.

name: Noivern
description: Noivern emits an explosive sound wave that attacks all nearby enemies and allies. The ultrasonic sound waves Noivern emits are strong enough to shatter large boulders.

name: Umbreon
description: Umbreon release the energy at night or when they are excited, and can use it to strike fear into bystanders to scare them away.

name: Lapras
description: With Water Absorb, Lapras can heal 1/4 of its max HP if it is hit with a Water-type attack. With the ability Shell Armor, Lapras can block any Critical Hits

name: Eevee
description: Eevee is said to have an irregularly-shaped genetic structure, enabling it to evolve into multiple Pokémon.

name: Greninja
description: Greninja use swift movements to confuse their enemies while they slice them up with throwing stars made of compressed water.

name: Milotic
description: Milotic has the ability to calm rage and strife among people.

name: Xerneas
description: Legends say it can share eternal life. It slept for a thousand years in the form of a tree before its revival.

name: Rayquaza
description: Rayquaza is commissioned with the natural duty of shielding Earth from meteorites and similar threats.

name: Mewtwo
description: As evidence of its immense power, Mewtwo is by far one of the most domineering Pokémon in the series.

name: Suicune
description: Suicune embodies the compassion of a pure spring of water. This Pokémon has the power to purify dirty water.

name: Charizard
description: Charizard seeks out stronger foes and only breathes fire during battles with worthy opponents. The fiery breath is so hot that it can turn any material to slag.

name: Pikachu
description: If someone pulls or steps on its tail, it is most likely it will bite or shock anyone in the area, including the one who pulled its tail.
